      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-201 Murderjoy&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 2 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the SGM-2 body, which is a flexible mainstay anti-ship missile.  This missile will deliver no payload.  It homes in on its target using a Passive Wake seeker.

