      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-2 ADASh Block V&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 2 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-2 body, which is a multi-purpose hybrid missile designed to penetrate point defense grids.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Passive Wake seeker.

